    • preInteract

      boolean preInteract​(Board board, java.util.ArrayList<Actor> enemies, Actor actor)
      A method which is used to fire events before the actor enters a space.
      参数:
      board - - the game board.
      enemies - - the enemies on the game board.
      actor - - the person doing the pre-move.
      返回:
      - true means continue to space, false means do not.
